					Currently working at TMMedia, prior to this I was working for BCPVA supervised by TMMedia. Before that and after during my studies I did a two month internship at ACL/Galvanize in Vancouver.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.heading-about {
		margin-left: 2rem;
	}
</style>
